What I learnt
theHarvester is a tool used to search public sources for things like emails, subdomains, hosts, and ip adresses attcahed to the domain put in the command. My domain had no exposed emails, nor any linkedin plaforms or published contact due to it being newly created and to be used as a test subject for this experiment. In reality, this could appear useful because little information brought out could mean that the domain has little footprint.
